{
  "texts": [
    "Conversely, we see that GPU energy increases upon quantization in Fig. 12.",
    "This increase is attributed to the increase in execution time when using a quantized pre-trained model.",
    "The model is dequantized once fetched from memory to align with GPU compute precision.",
    "We see similar observations for 3D-TPU where overall system energy increases after quantization.",
    "HAIMA also observes an increase in energy with the dequantization operation necessary for the model to be executed within DRAM banks."
  ]
}